casebody.data:
COLORADO DEPARTMENT OF STATE, Petitioner
v.
Micheal BACA, et al. No. 19-518 Supreme Court of the United States. January 27, 2020

Petitioner in No. 19-465 and respondent in No. 19-518 shall file opening and reply briefs on the merits under the schedule set forth in Rules 25.1 and 25.3. Respondent in No. 19-465 and petitioner in No. 19-518 shall file response briefs on the merits under the schedule set forth in Rule 25.2.
